data.title: Wells Fargo Bank and Express Office
data.meta_description: The ruins of the Wells Fargo Bank and Express Office on C Street in Virginia City. The Hotel Virginia is to the left, and the Virginia City National Guard Hall beyond that. These buildings have all been demolished. The spire of St. Mary's Church is in the distance on the right.
